## Features

**Chat Interface:**
- Real-time messaging with AI agent
- Color-coded messages (blue user, white assistant)
- Code block formatting
- Smooth animations

**Sidebar:**
- Quick action buttons
- Live stats (problems solved, mastery score)
- Tips and guidance

**Error Handling:**
- User-friendly messages
- Icons for clarity (üîå ‚ö†Ô∏è ‚ùå)
- Actionable fix instructions

**Loading Feedback:**
- Visual spinner
- Progress text
- Time estimates
- No blank screens

